<HEADER>
A5006 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w BC-HEALTH-BLACKS-0125-CO     01-24 0615
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-HEALTH-BLACKS-0125-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    BLACK PHYSICIANS SAY MANAGED-CARE PLAN RACIALLY BIASED
 &HT;    (400&AMP;ADD)
