   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   FBN-PATRIOTS (Boston) -- Dom Capers and Tom Donahoe, the
coach/general manager duo who may have moved from Plan B to Plan A
on the Patriots' priority list, will interview in New England
Tuesday. By Nick Cafardo. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
