r p BC-BUSH-CAPITALPUNISHMEN     01-24 1250
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BUSH-CAPITALPUNISHMENT-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
GOVERNOR TURNS DEAF EAR TO FOES OF DEATH PENALTY
</HEADLINE>
 (Resending to fix coding) 
(For use by NYTimes News Service Clients) 
By JOHN MORITZ 
c.2000 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
