<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: adds new 10th graf updating with Miami relatives planning
to go to Washington ...
 &HT;    ELIAN'S GRANDMOTHER FLY TO MIAMI, REUNION UNCERTAIN
 &HT;    (900&AMP;ADD)
 &HT;    With Photos.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By MIKE WILLIAMS 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
